9 An act relating to creating the Office of New Americans Study Committee
10 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
11 Sec. 1. OFFICE OF NEW AMERICANS STUDY COMMITTEE; REPORT
12 (a) Creation. There is created the Office of New Americans Study
13 Committee to make recommendations for creating an independent Office of
14 New Americans.
15 (b) Membership. The Committee shall be composed of the following
16 members:
17 (1) the Director of the Vermont Refugee Office, who shall be Chair;
18 (2) one current member of the House of Representatives, who shall be
19 appointed by the Speaker of the House;
